  "text": "As we already said, the model studied here, inspired from [CITATION_1] , falls into the class of \"Aw-Rascle\" models. So we could use the approach and the theoretical results of [3] , which should apply here with minor modifications. However, our approach is different: here, contrarily to the above reference, we establish directly a connection between the Follow-The-Leader model in Section 4 and the macroscopic system (1.4), without viewing both systems as issued from a same fully discrete system (Godunov scheme) with different limits, and without passing in Lagrangian coordinates. For related works, including vacuum, see also [2, [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
